measurements.description: One flat flower on one 9.5-cm inflorescence; sepals white veined green; petals slightly undulate, white heavily veined green, burgundy line midrib fading to spots proximally, overlaid rose distally, margins hirsuite, raised bugundy spots proximal half; pouch yellow-green overlaid dark rose, heavily veined dark green; staminode green; substance medium; texture waxy.
